The recent increase in shares of
 Glencore International Plc (GLEN)  and  Xstrata Plc (XTA)  indicates markets see
their merger as a balanced operation, Xstrata Executive Director
Santiago Zaldumbide told  ABC  newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
